{"tid":1306820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林卓廷質疑「一周一行」限制失效　保安局迴避處理問題","createTime":"2019-07-11T09:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T19:10:14.000Z","uid":13867,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a236bd4279a34352de94664a4352b8a35f3d568d","tid":1306820,"uid":13867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"林卓廷質疑「一周一行」限制失效 保安局迴避處理問題<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷表示，接獲入境處前線人員投訴，內地人可以利用「個人遊」簽注，短時間內多次入境香港，令到「一周一行」的限制變相失效，質疑保安局「裝聾扮啞」，迴避處理有關問題。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷說，上月初派員到內地視察，證實透過「自助簽注機」，只需三分鐘便可以申請簽注來港，續簽次數亦沒有限制。他表示，漏洞使內地人可以長期居留香港，香港與內地邊界變相消失，會令水貨、黑工及賣淫問題更嚴重，令民怨升溫。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷說，曾向保安局查詢有關情況，局方回覆指，未能提供內地人透過「個人遊」來港的具體數字。他質疑保安局不可能不知道漏洞存在，要求盡快與內地商討，堵塞漏洞。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，可以無限loop無限留，一千萬人口不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係李家超，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c76ccd89781b9adac6a6a612170043f1fca0a6","tid":1306820,"uid":55130,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府有無咁撚多bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75dacff617078d20d1918899755e8152985e6f3e","tid":1306820,"uid":13867,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"04c76ccd89781b9adac6a6a612170043f1fca0a6","tid":1306820,"uid":55130,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府有無咁撚多bug<img src=\"/assets/fac